| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2026-1506 — Recovery Inhibition (interlock)"
| comment "Status: stable | Level: high | ID: 9dae32e1-bb5d-558b-ac3f-6af94ed1aa9b"
